snippet.textDisplay:
I've been listening non-stop to this song, it's related to my story. A best friend of mine had feeling for me and he treated me too good, he cared for me just like I'm his family, but at that time I never realized, I just thought of him as a "normal" friend. And finally when I realized, I had to move to another place. The last moment of us, we couldn't say anything, I knew he wanted to say something and I wanted too, but we just leant against the wall, not even able to look at the other.
I lost all of his contact and I still deeply regret everything. I just wish one day when we are able to meet again, I could be a friend.
Sweet Night is sad, especially the part "I wonder if you are too good to be true", I can be related. Taehyung's voice is forever my favorite, he is my pride and our most precious, I'm glad that he has us army and the members with him. 💜
